title: RGP-2: Liquidity Mining Program
body:
We recently proposed RGP-2, Ribbon's first liquidity mining program. This program will go live June 15 2021 12:00pm UTC and run until July 15 2021 12:00pm UTC. 

To read more about the proposal, see [here](https://gov.ribbon.finance/t/rgp-2-ribbon-liquidity-mining-program/90).
